Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.34,0:00:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦前往Altair…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.78,0:00:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女性要麼就死 要麼就變成男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼說Mix也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已經不再是我們所認識的Mix了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連記憶都喪失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡和柚葉沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體檢結果也沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在那裡再多待一會兒的話 我們也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃還沒有回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.61,0:00:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她出去找不動總司令還沒回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特的情況怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.22,0:00:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說暫時脫離生命危險
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.36,0:00:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但需要靜養
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.35,0:00:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總司令不在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.81,0:00:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特也因用盡了力量而臥病在床
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Neo DEAVA已經不行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.30,0:00:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要輕易放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.75,0:01:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並非到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重整旗鼓 再度進軍Altair界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.84,0:01:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要救出Mix
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.10,0:01:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安迪 不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奪回Mix之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直…一直窮追不捨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:29.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.73,0:01:36.78,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反転する世界のプラトニック 愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:52.43,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らが見てる世界は いつでも逆さまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:02:02.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうしようもないことで たいがい決まってく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:14.98,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙するほど傷つく瞳 心で叫びながら黙っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:25.57,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後のふたり 混ざれないまま 秒読みが聞こえてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:31.73,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.99,0:02:37.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すたれゆく動物みたいに愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:41.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泣きたいくらい君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:45.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反転する世界のプラトニック
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:48.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感じたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:29.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美得令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.73,0:01:36.78,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們在倒錯的精神世界中相愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:52.43,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們眼裡的世界總是相互顛倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:02:02.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幾乎要被認定為是無可奈何的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:14.98,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口淌淚的眼眸 在內心沉默地叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:25.57,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的兩人來不及結合便聽到離別的倒數
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:31.73,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美得令人絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.99,0:02:37.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們像漸趨衰老的動物一樣相愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:41.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美得令人落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.09,0:02:45.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在倒錯的精神世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:48.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想細細體會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:03:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:03:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差一點就能看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.65,0:03:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個世界合奏究極的愛的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在優先養好身體
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能在生命之火熄滅之前完成曲子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告訴我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過你的絕望預知
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕望的未來什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有些旋律正因在絕望中演奏才顯得優美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.61,0:03:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲子完成了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能和我一起演奏嗎 摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動總司令什麼時候才會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃那邊也沒有任何聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一個如何 須緒美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不了 深夜進食高熱量的東西有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.50,0:04:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有慌張的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不動肯定會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.17,0:04:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連同創聖的神話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草綠色頭髮的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得幫你打開了次元門
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你履行約定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我許下了什麼約定?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在想不起來也不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.06,0:04:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待時機一成熟 約定自然會得以履行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.73,0:05:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mix…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那時已算是看過她的大胸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛…雖然完全不是大胸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安迪 你在這裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不坐在這裡的話我會下沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是…Mix填補的洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.02,0:05:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙填補過的地方的分子結構完全沒有間隙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就算我的力量失控也不會隨便下沉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算把Mix奪回來…我對Mix…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對變成了男人的Mix…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能一如既往地保持愛意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說怎麼會沒有味道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.31,0:06:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於合為一體了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿波隆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這邊 阿波隆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們終於能相見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來接我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:06:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭女人 我們不是什麼阿波隆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿馬神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別走 臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也和我合為一體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.56,0:08:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合掌之間有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手和右手 天使和人 男人和女人 陰和陽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其狹縫裡到底有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在於左右手狹縫間的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.17,0:08:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什麼都沒有 卻好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這好像之前也在哪裡聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:08:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天地初開後不久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界充滿著美麗的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花草在歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往來不斷的昆蟲和聖獸在細說情話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天使在繁星閃耀的高空中共諧連理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而可怕的是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些天使是會狩獵人類的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬥爭中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為殺戮天使的阿波羅尼亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邂逅了名叫瑟利雅的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人隨即墜入愛河
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿波羅尼亞斯背叛了同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站到了人類的一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後罪人阿波羅尼亞斯捨棄了翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和人類一起操縱著巨大的力量--機械天使
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.89,0:09:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和眾天使戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是創聖之書流所記載的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一萬二千年前的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這是時間追溯到再上一個輪迴…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二萬四千年前的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後命運再度輪迴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神話將再次被傳承
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神話將再次…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔·空 你想怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.93,0:10:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不記得有下達出擊命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不允許你擅自行動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺她在呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃在向我求救
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我必須快點出發
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再目送重要的人的背影…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 到你心愛之人的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後回到太陽之翼的身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一半的你 是時候睜開眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.24,0:11:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Z
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然切斷著通信 所在位置也不明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用你的絕望預知確定阿馬塔的位置嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和御子乃初次邂逅的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.81,0:12:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創聖之書所述的光與暗狹縫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛艙裡面空空如也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和阿馬塔初次邂逅的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時也是我們初次合體的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那場戰鬥過後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有聽說過這裡被認定為嚴重監視區域
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到居然會變成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃也在這一帶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的預知是這麼告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然是追著御子乃來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們暫且先分頭尋找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有這麼多…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我貼的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.74,0:14:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡到底有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未影為什麼讓我到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這氣味…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.95,0:14:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前 我來過這座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶的封印 總算被解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Aquaria舞動於空」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡 你怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.24,0:16:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是追著阿馬塔過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉克蕾雅理事長的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.66,0:16:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟怪炎一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…抱歉 因為我無視了命令…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座城市 現在被認定為嚴重監視區域
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說已下達了避難命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 所以老闆他們也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不惜違反命令也要到這座城市來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺御子乃在呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.90,0:17:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會一直等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕要等一萬二千年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔之前是在這個電影院裡工作的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在這裡邂逅了御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.06,0:17:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個…下一個一萬二千年後…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要經人類之手編撰的虛假故事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過不久真正的神話就會在這世上甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 奔跑吧 愛的野獸們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔往約定之地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 拔不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管我了 阿馬塔你快逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我不能丟下婕希卡不管
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:19:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿馬塔 找你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 怪炎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山茶花?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Y? 莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是約好曲子完成了的話就一起演奏的嗎 摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 以那種身體狀態合體的話 你的生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.35,0:20:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間猶豫了 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捨身合體 GO Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要腐壞了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion SPADA
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 窩囊廢阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽之翼如今正準備覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了很過分的事情 原諒我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…難道那時候看到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我還以為是幻影什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.51,0:22:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一事無成的窩囊廢阿馬塔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.23,0:22:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.09,0:22:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.02,0:22:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.20,0:00:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------ED-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:59.45,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}君へ続く坂道に 白い花が咲いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.59,0:23:07.26,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}夢から覚めたあとも 悲しい空見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.75,0:23:17.24,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}この気持ち葉っぱの裏に住んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.10,0:23:26.74,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}朝露が落ちる音に 耳をすませてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:34.60,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神様 あなたが造った世界は 完璧じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:42.19,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}ここでは毎日恋がポロポロ 死んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.39,0:23:46.38,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}はじめて好きになったの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.53,0:23:49.54,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}あなたは知らないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.67,0:23:54.07,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}地球の裏側でいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.25,0:23:57.28,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.47,0:24:01.61,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}私を忘れてもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.83,0:24:08.12,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:59.45,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}延伸到你身旁的坡道 點綴著雪白色的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.59,0:23:07.26,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}從睡夢中驚醒之後 遠望著憂傷的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.75,0:23:17.24,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}這份青澀的感覺 依存在綠葉錯綜的紋路之間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.10,0:23:26.74,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}側耳聆聽 晨露緩緩落下的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:34.60,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神明您所創造的這個世界並不完美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:42.19,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}因為這裡每天都有戀情一段接一段地告終
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.39,0:23:46.38,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我是初嘗戀愛的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.53,0:23:49.54,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}這個你應該不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.67,0:23:54.07,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}即便永不見天日也沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.25,0:23:57.28,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我只希望你留在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.47,0:24:01.61,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}就算你把我忘卻也沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.83,0:24:08.12,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我只希望你留在我身邊
